 043:     # -------- Case 1 (most likely) --------
 044:     #   two indep. columns, geometric multiplicitiy: 1
 045:     #   -> the column space has rank 2
 046:     # idea:
 047:     #   use two of the vectors spanning the column space to find the egVector
 048:     #   by taking the cross product
 049:     # implementation:
 050:     #   take cross product of two random vectors.
 051:     #   If the cross product is zero, they are parallell, which won't work. If so,
